  TD 0.0034  Tc 0  Tw (--) Tj6.72 0  TD 0.0319  Tc -0.1519  Tw ( the dark rain clouds of the sky.) Tj131.04 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-381.6 -11.52  TD 0.0451  Tc -0.1651  Tw (12 Out of the brightness of his presence clouds advanced, with hailstones and bolts of lightning.) Tj399.36 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-399.36 -11.52  TD 0.0047  Tc -0.1247  Tw (13 The LORD thundered from heaven; the voice) Tj200.64 0  TD 0.022  Tc -0.142  Tw ( of the Most High resounded.) Tj120.96 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-321.6 -11.52  TD 0.0361  Tc -0.1561  Tw (14 He shot his arrows and scattered, great bolts of lightning and routed them.) Tj322.56 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-322.56 -11.52  TD 0.0275  Tc 0.9325  Tw (15 The valleys of the sea were exposed and the foundations of the earth laid bare at your rebuke, O ) Tj0 -11.52  TD -0  Tc -0.1194  Tw (LORD, at the blast of breath from your nostrils.) Tj197.28 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-197.28 -11.52  TD 0.0016  Tc -0.1216  Tw (16 He reached down from on high and took hold of me; he drew me out of deep waters.) Tj360 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-360 -11.52  TD -0.0719  Tc -0.0481  Tw (17 He rescued me from my powerful enemy, from my foes, who were too strong for me.) Tj354.24 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-354.24 -11.52  TD 0.0088  Tc -0.1288  Tw (18 They confronted me in the day of my disaster, but the LORD was my support.) Tj331.68 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-331.68 -11.52  TD -0.0304  Tc -0.0896  Tw (19 He brou) Tj47.04 0  TD 0.0163  Tc -0.1363  Tw (ght me out into a spacious place; he rescued me because he delighted in me.) Tj314.88 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-361.92 -11.52  TD 0.0182  Tc -0.1115  Tw (20 The LORD has dealt with me according to my righteousness; according to the cleanness of my hands ) Tj0 -11.52  TD 0.0075  Tc -0.1275  Tw (he has rewarded me.) Tj85.44 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-85.44 -11.52  TD -0.0068  Tc -0.1132  Tw (21 For I have kept the ways of the LORD; I have not done evi) Tj253