 enthroned as the Holy One; you are the praise of Israel.) Tj291.84 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-291.84 -11.52  TD 0.0172  Tc -0.1372  Tw (4   In you our fathers put their trust; they trusted and you delivered them.) Tj303.36 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-303.36 -11.52  TD 0.0167  Tc -0.1367  Tw (5   They cried to you and were saved; in you they trusted and w) Tj259.68 0  TD 0.0565  Tc -0.1765  Tw (ere not disappointed.) Tj86.88 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-346.56 -11.52  TD 0.0313  Tc -0.1513  Tw (6   But I am a worm and not a man, scorned by men and despised by the people.) Tj330.24 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-330.24 -11.04  TD 0.0181  Tc -0.1381  Tw (7   All who see me mock me; they hurl insults, shaking their heads:) Tj277.92 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-277.92 -11.52  TD 0.0009  Tc -0.1209  Tw (8   "He trusts in the LORD; let the LORD rescue him. Let him deliver him, since he delig) Tj367.68 0  TD 0.0022  Tc -0.1222  Tw (hts in him.") Tj50.4 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-418.08 -11.52  TD -0.0144  Tc -0.1056  Tw (9   Yet you brought me out of the womb; you made me trust in you even at my mother\222s breast.) Tj387.36 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-387.36 -11.52  TD -0.0216  Tc -0.0984  Tw (10  From birth I was cast upon you; from my mother\222s womb you have been my God.) Tj348.96 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-348.96 -11.52  TD -0.0119  Tc -0.1081  Tw (11  Do not be far from me, for trouble is near and there is no one to ) Tj280.32 0  TD 0.1356  Tc 0  Tw (help.) Tj20.64 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-300.96 -11.52  TD 0.0277  Tc -0.1477  Tw (12  Many bulls surround me; strong bulls of Bashan encircle me.) Tj271.2 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-271.2 -11.52  TD 0.0337  Tc -0.1537  Tw (13  Roaring lions tearing their prey open their mouths wide against me.) Tj297.12 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-297.12 -11.52  TD 0.0382  Tc 0.6218  Tw (14  I am poured out like water, and all my bones are out of joint. My heart has turned to wax; it has ) Tj0 -11.