ained the suffering of the afflicted one; he has not hidden his face ) Tj0 -11.52  TD 0.0155  Tc -0.1355  Tw (from him but has listened to his cry for help.) Tj183.84 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-183.84 -11.04  TD -0.0269  Tc 0.0269  Tw (25  From you comes the theme of my praise in the gr) Tj217.44 0  TD -0.0054  Tc -0.1146  Tw (eat assembly; before those who fear you will I fulfill ) Tj-217.44 -11.52  TD -0.1311  Tc 0.0111  Tw (my vows.) Tj36.48 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-36.48 -11.52  TD 0.0319  Tc 0.5981  Tw (26  The poor will eat and be satisfied; they who seek the LORD will praise him) Tj337.44 0  TD 0.0034  Tc 0  Tw (--) Tj6.72 0  TD -0.0235  Tc 0.2875  Tw ( may your hearts live ) Tj-344.16 -11.52  TD -0.1183  Tc 0  Tw (forever!) Tj32.64 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-32.64 -11.52  TD 0.0444  Tc -0.1644  Tw (27  All the ends of the earth will remember and turn to the LORD, and all the fam) Tj339.84 0  TD 0.0216  Tc -0.5256  Tw (ilies of the nations will ) Tj-339.84 -11.52  TD -0.017  Tc -0.103  Tw (bow down before him,) Tj91.2 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-91.2 -11.52  TD 0.0104  Tc -0.1304  Tw (28  for dominion belongs to the LORD and he rules over the nations.) Tj284.64 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-284.64 -11.52  TD 0.0327  Tc 0.2619  Tw (29  All the rich of the earth will feast and worship; all who go down to the dust will kneel before him) Tj425.28 0  TD 0.0034  Tc 0  Tw (--) Tj6.72 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-432 -11.52  TD -0.0082  Tc -0.1118  Tw (those who cannot keep themselves al) Tj151.2 0  TD -0.0883  Tc 0  Tw (ive.) Tj13.92 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-165.12 -11.52  TD 0.0239  Tc -0.1439  Tw (30  Posterity will serve him; future generations will be told about the Lord.) Tj308.64 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-308.64 -11.52  TD 0.0194  Tc -0.1394  Tw (31  They will proclaim his righteousness to a people yet unborn) Tj262.08 0  TD 0.0034  Tc 0  Tw (--) Tj6.72 0  TD 0.0021  Tc -0.1221  Tw ( for he has done it.) Tj77.28 0  T