 -0.6  Tw ( ) Tj335.52 0  TD -0.0738  Tc 0.9138  Tw (is not the only ) Tj-371.52 -11.52  TD -0.0416  Tc 0.1616  Tw (interpretation of the new song, God put on our mouths. A new song stands for an original composition; it is ) Tj0 -11.52  TD -0.0685  Tc 0.7485  Tw (a hymn that evolves from our own personality and that fits our character. It is in the act of bowing before ) TjT* -0.1056  Tc 0.9456  Tw (God, and in the praising) Tj98.4 0  TD -0.0885  Tc 0.6461  Tw ( of His Name that we discover who and what we are. We begin to understand that ) Tj-98.4 -11.52  TD -0.0732  Tc -0.0468  Tw (this is the purpose for which we were made.) Tj174.24 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-138.24 -11.52  TD -0.074  Tc 0.914  Tw (The phrase \223a new song\224 is found repeatedly in the Book of Psalms .) Tj283.68 4.32  TD /F0 6.72  Tf0  Tc 0  Tw (763) Tj10.08 -4.32  TD /F0 10.08  Tf-0.1326  Tc 0.4926  Tw ( The elders and the living ) Tj-329.76 -11.04  TD -0.0342  Tc 0.3942  Tw (creatures in the book of Revelation si) Tj151.68 0  TD -0.0684  Tc 0.3255  Tw (ng a new song, and so do the 144.000 redeemed who stand before the ) Tj-151.68 -11.52  TD -0.0621  Tc 0  Tw (throne.) Tj27.84 4.32  TD /F0 6.72  Tf0  Tc (764) Tj10.08 -4.32  TD /F0 10.08  Tf-0.0845  Tc 1.6571  Tw ( We do not sing solos in heaven. We are part of God\222s new creation, which praises God and ) Tj-37.92 -11.52  TD -0.0474  Tc 0.9941  Tw (glorifies Him. It is \223a hymn of praise to our God.\224 Praising God makes us realize that we a) Tj378.24 0  TD -0.0492  Tc 0.6492  Tw (re part of the ) Tj-378.24 -11.52  TD -0.0749  Tc 0.7092  Tw (body, which is the result of our baptism with the Holy Spirit. Paul says: \223For we were all baptized by one ) Tj0 -11.52  TD -0.0475  Tc 1.8475  Tw (Spirit into one body) Tj84.48 0  TD 0.0034  Tc 0  Tw (--) Tj6.72 0  TD -0.0768  Tc 1.8768  Tw ( whether Jews or Greeks, slave or free) Tj164.16 0  TD 0.0034  Tc 0  Tw (--) Tj6.72 0  TD -0.0818  Tc 1.5458  Tw ( and we were a