m God and not from ) Tj0 -11.52  TD -0.0676  Tc 0.8733  Tw (men. God usually uses men to help us; but this does in no way a) Tj265.92 0  TD -0.0427  Tc 0.3547  Tw (nnul the fact that the source of all help is ) Tj-265.92 -11.52  TD -0.0686  Tc 0.9086  Tw (God Himself. And we should never come to the point that we expect supernatural help from mortal men, ) Tj0 -11.52  TD -0.0919  Tc -0.0281  Tw (especially not from those who have openly turned away from God.) Tj263.52 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-227.52 -11.52  TD -0.0768  Tc 0.4368  Tw (Realizing what God has done for us is an exper) Tj191.04 0  TD -0.0545  Tc 0.24  Tw (ience just as awesome as when we look up into the ) Tj-227.04 -11.52  TD -0.1011  Tc 1.0455  Tw (night sky and try to imagine in what kind of a universe we live. Once we fix our eyes upon God, we see ) Tj0 -11.52  TD -0.0619  Tc -0.0581  Tw (how His relationship with us is expressed in an endless series of supernatural interventions. ) Tj364.32 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-364.32 -29.28  TD (                              ) Tj72 0  TD (                              ) TjET89.76 155.04 144 0.48 re fBT234.24 152.64  TD( ) Tj-144 -8.16  TD /F0 8.16  Tf0.24  Tc 0  Tw (763) Tj12.96 -5.28  TD /F0 12  Tf-0.1448  Tc 0.0248  Tw ( See Ps 33:3; 40:3; ) Tj90.24 0  TD -0.192  Tc 0.072  Tw (96:1; 98:1; 144:9; and 149:1.) Tj134.4 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-237.6 -21.6  TD /F0 6.72  Tf0  Tw (764) Tj10.08 -4.32  TD /F0 10.08  Tf-0.0058  Tc -0.1142  Tw ( See Rev 5:9; 14:3) Tj73.92 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-84 -8.16  TD /F0 8.16  Tf0.24  Tc 0  Tw (765) Tj12.96 -5.28  TD /F0 12  Tf-0.1452  Tc 0.0252  Tw ( I Cor. 12:13) Tj59.52 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-72.48 -21.12  TD /F0 6.72  Tf0  Tw (766) Tj10.08 -4.32  TD /F0 10.08  Tf0.0357  Tc -0.1557  Tw ( Acts 25:10) Tj46.56 0  TD 0.0034  Tc 0  Tw (-) Tj3.36 0  TD 0.24  Tc (12) Tj10.56 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) TjETendstreamendobj644 0 obj9935 endobj645 0 obj<< /Type /Page